If children learn multiple languages, especially the languages of developing countries, they will have more opportunities to find a good job.
In Scotland, each school offers a variety of languages.
Some schools will include classic, modern languages in their program, while others will opt for the languages considered to be the most important in the UK in 2020, for example Mandarin or Japanese.
Regardless of the interests of your child, in independent schools will always have a varied selection, as well as teaching staff who are competent in this field.
